Summary of sim_data object

Source: R/summary.sim_data.R
summary.sim_data.Rd

Summary of sim_data object

Usage

# S3 method for sim_data
summary(object, ...)

Arguments

object

sim_data object; returned by initialise function

...

further arguments passed to or from other methods; currently none specified

Value

summary.sim_data object

Examples


# data preparation
library(terra)

n1_small <- rast(system.file("input_maps/n1_small.tif", package = "rangr"))
K_small <- rast(system.file("input_maps/K_small.tif", package = "rangr"))

sim_data <- initialise(
  n1_map = n1_small,
  K_map = K_small,
  r = log(2),
  rate = 1 / 1e3
)
#> NaN values were found in input maps and replaced with NA (cells outside the study area)
summary(sim_data)
